(21806, 29303, 0, 1, '牧羊人', '寫給自私自利的人', '2009-10-22 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 9, 'Waiting and depending solve noting.\r\n\r\n等待與依賴，不能夠解決問題\r\n\r\nWhy don’t people introspection themself.\r\n\r\n為什麼不想想自己的過錯\r\n\r\nAnger, sorrow and destruction.\r\n\r\n憤怒、悲傷以及破壞\r\n\r\nThey don’t make things up.\r\n\r\n也已經於事無補\r\n\r\nThe cross, to me.\r\n\r\n這十字架，就我而論\r\n\r\nThe world has been nailed on the cross.\r\n\r\n世界，已經釘在十字架上\r\n\r\nTo the world.\r\n\r\n對世界而論\r\n\r\nI’ve been nailed on the cross.\r\n\r\n我已經釘在十字架上\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n副歌\r\n\r\nI’m a shepheard dying for sheeps.\r\n\r\n我是一個牧羊人，為羊而捨命\r\n\r\nI believe in my sheep, and they belive in me, too.\r\n\r\n我相信我的羊，我的羊也相信我\r\n\r\nFollowing me through my voice.\r\n\r\n他們聽著我的聲音，跟著我\r\n\r\nYou don’t believe in me, because you’re not my sheeps.\r\n\r\n你們不會相信，因為你們不是我的羊\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n☆\r\n\r\n我 就是 牧羊人\r\n\r\n可以拯救你們同樣可以摧毀你們\r\n\r\n哦 不用耍狠 早已經看透你們\r\n\r\n看了兩千年都煩了 有點水準\r\n\r\n', '', 222, '', '開睿', '阿能', '亮亮', 'TBH鐵皮屋', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-02-10 23:47:32', '2013-10-07 17:15:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
